historyControl.load.shortDescription: Load in user data for history storage.

params.name: url
params.description: URL of page to add to history listing.

params.name: title
params.description: Title of page to add to history listing in form of a string. If there is no title, then the value should be `null`. Default: `null`.

params.name: date
params.description: Date at point of page load to add to history listing. Default: `new Date()`.

params.name: removeDuplicates
params.description: Whether to remove recent duplicates in the history listing (for example, to prevent page refreshes from being stored). Default: `true`.
